#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=You mentioned Australia being like a country of summer sports .
#Text=What attracted you to winter sport in the first place ?
#Text=I think it 's a better sport .
#Text=( laughter )
#Text=Australians , considering we do n't have many hills , Australians do love skiing , those that do it .

#Text=It 's a unique sport in the sense that you get to travel at high speeds , on different mountains all over the world , under your own power , going down a hill at 130 or something k 's an hour , that sort of thing .
#Text=You do n't get ... to me , running up and down a track , or ...
#Text=I think to me it 's a fun sport .
#Text=There are n't that many sports that people , a lot of people , spend heaps of their own money to go and do , as a pastime .
#Text=As something that they want to do on the holidays and with their family and all that kind of stuff .
#Text=It 's kind of cool that that 's what we do .
#Text=Like , lots of people would spend a sh-tload of money to go skiing , and that 's our sport .
#Text=Not many people would pay a heap of money to stare at a black line in a pool , or to run around a track against the clock .
#Text=Yeah , we love it , and that 's why I 've done it for so many years , because I love the sport .

#Text=I mean , racing 's one thing but if I did n't enjoy skiing I would n't be here and there 's not a day when ... I mean you have cold days and weather and stuff , but you do n't ... for us to get out and get on the hill is n't a burden I do n't think in the same way as other sports can be .

#Text=I think the change for me — I think I can speak for Cam as well , ' cause he 's been around for a while — the change between racing in so many classes to racing in so few probably kept us around , I think .

#Text=It made it a lot more competitive ; it made it a lot more of a challenge , that previously it would n't have been , and I think if we took an LW2 class right now we 'd be getting similar results to what Michael got in Salt Lake City , so , the fact that it did get a lot more competitive is probably why I 've been here for so long , in the challenge to keep competing and keep improving and keep performing at the highest level .
#Text=Are there any skiers that you 're looking forward to racing against this week coming up ?
